description:
The shorter Grappler has only seen TAG TEAM ACTION in the last few months, but she's well rested and eager to advance. She's a style point whore - If she gets you in a hold she will score style on you.
The Assassin has been doing very well at US lately, she found her groove, and is a serious case to be reckoned with. If you lose the Assassin you are going to get the life fucked out of you, and that is not a threat, it is a promise.
title: SUMMER VENGEANCE
